text.section:
The description of the Alzheimer's special care unit or program shall include:
A statement of philosophy or mission;
Staff training and staff job titles;
Admission procedures including screening criteria;
Assessment and care planning protocol;
Staffing patterns;
A description of the physical environment and any unique design features appropriate to support the functioning of cognitively impaired individuals;
A description of activities including frequency and type;
Charges to residents for services provided by the Alzheimer's special care unit or program;
Discharge procedures;
Any services, training, or other procedures that are over and above those that are provided in the existing assisted living program; and
Any other information that the Department may require.
